新的电视调查显示英国最受欢迎的吉他即兴演奏https://www.nme.com/news/tv/uk-favourite-guitar-riff-revealed-3552047?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=uk-favourite-guitar-riff-revealedAlex Berry Fri, 01 Dec 2023 14:06:02 +0000 Music NewsNewsTV NewsIndiePopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3552047 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/guns-n-roses-guitar.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="枪与玫瑰乐队" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/guns-n-roses-guitar.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/guns-n-roses-guitar-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/guns-n-roses-guitar-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/guns-n-roses-guitar-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/guns-n-roses-guitar-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/guns-n-roses-guitar-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Sam Fender、Arctic Monkeys 和 Prince 跻身前 40 名</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/uk-favourite-guitar-riff-revealed-3552047">新的电视调查显示英国最受欢迎的吉他连复</a>段首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/guns-n-roses-guitar.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="枪与玫瑰乐队" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/guns-n-roses-guitar.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/guns-n-roses-guitar-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/guns-n-roses-guitar-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/guns-n-roses-guitar-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/guns-n-roses-guitar-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/guns-n-roses-guitar-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.skygroup.sky/article/sky-arts-discovers-the-nation-s-greatest-guitar-riff-of-all-time">Sky Arts</a>在 11 月 24 日播出的全新三部分纪录片系列<em>《最伟大的吉他即兴演奏》</em>中揭示了英国最受欢迎的吉他即兴演奏。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sam-fender-seventeen-going-under-review-3060680">萨姆·芬德 (Sam Fender) – 《十七岁的沉沦》评论：艺术家年轻时的肖像</a></li></ul><p>一项针对 2000 名乐迷投票的民意调查旨在找出全国最喜欢的即兴重复段，进入前 40 名的是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-fender">Sam Fender</a>的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sam-fender-seventeen-going-under-review-3060680">Seventeen Going Under</a> 》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arctic-monkeys">Arctic Moneys 的</a>《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/arctic-monkeys-133-1250909">Do I Wanna Know</a> 》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pharrell-williams">Pharrell William</a>的《快乐的&#39;。</p><p>但最佳选择是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/guns-n-roses">Guns N&#39; Roses</a>的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guns-n-roses-sweet-child-o-mine-surpasses-one-billion-streams-on-spotify-3014987">Sweet Child O&#39; Mine</a> 》。这首歌曲于 1988 年 6 月发行，很快就登上了美国 Billboard Hot 100 排行榜的榜首，成为该摇滚乐队唯一的美国冠军单曲。</p><p>它在<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-lists/best-songs-of-all-time-1224767/guns-n-roses-sweet-child-o-mine-1225250/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石杂志</em></a>2021 年<em>有史以来最伟大的 500 首歌曲</em>排行榜上排名第 88 位，显然仍然是英国公众的最爱。 </p><figure id="attachment_3552065" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3552065" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3552065" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/brian-may-guitar.jpg" alt="布莱恩·梅" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/brian-may-guitar.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/brian-may-guitar-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/brian-may-guitar-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/brian-may-guitar-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/brian-may-guitar-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/brian-may-guitar-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3552065" class="wp-caption-text"> 2016 年 5 月 22 日，Queen 乐队的布莱恩·梅 (Brian May) 在西班牙巴塞罗那。图片来源：Getty/摄影：Jordi Vidal/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/prince">Prince</a>的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/20-things-you-didnt-know-about-purple-rain-766800">Purple Rain</a> 》获得亚军，英国摇滚乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dire-straits">Dire Straits</a>的《Sultans Of Swing》获得第三名。</p><p>天空艺术总监菲尔·埃德加·琼斯在谈到该系列节目时表示：“无论是已故的伟大<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jimi-hendrix">吉米·亨德里克斯</a>，还是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/iron-maiden">铁娘子</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/led-zeppelin">齐柏林飞艇</a>等中坚力量，还是新晋艺术家，摇滚乐永远不会死。”</p><p> “不断有新的人才涌现。人们对新曲子和甜美即兴重复的胃口一如既往地大，”他继续说道。</p><p>但古典音乐仍然取得了胜利，民意调查发现<a href="https://www.google.com/search?client=safari&amp;rls=en&amp;q=nme+queen&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;oe=UTF-8">皇后</a>乐队的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brian-may">布莱恩·梅</a>击败了亨德里克斯和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eric-clapton">埃里克·克莱普顿</a>，被评为有史以来最伟大的吉他手。</p><p>根据 30% 的参与者的说法，吉他即兴演奏的“黄金时代”是在 1970 年代，而 21% 的人认为 1980 年代更为优越。</p><p>该剧由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-sabbath">Black Sabbath</a>的吉他传奇人物<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tony-iommi">Tony Iommi</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-police">The Police</a>的 Andy Summers 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/heart">Heart</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nancy-wilson">Nancy Wilson</a>主演。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/heart">Bon Jovi</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-killers">The Killers</a>和许多其他传奇乐队的吉他明星也加入了他们的行列，探索吉他连复段对音乐史的影响。</p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bon-jovi-share-new-original-song-christmas-isnt-christmas-listen-3544230">邦乔维发行了一首原创圣诞歌曲</a>，名为“圣诞节不是圣诞节”。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/uk-favourite-guitar-riff-revealed-3552047">新的电视调查显示英国最受欢迎的吉他连复</a>段首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
